CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Treasure Global Inc has created an online-to-offline e-commerce platform business model offering consumers and merchants instant rebates and affiliate cashback programs, while providing a seamless e-payment solution with rebates in both e-commerce and physical retailers/merchant settings. Its product is an internet application branded ZCITY app, that targets consumers by providing personalized deals based on consumers' purchase history, location and preferences.
